m:agent="v1"><span begin="0:31.050" end="0:32.012">感情是</span><span begin="0:32.012" end="0:33.007">偏</span><span begin="0:33.007" end="0:33.672">执</span><span begin="0:33.672" end="0:34.605">的</span></p><p begin="0:35.821" end="0:39.797" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:35.821" end="0:37.259">越爱越是</span><span begin="0:37.259" end="0:38.238">偏</span><span begin="0:38.238" end="0:38.898">执</span><span begin="0:38.898" end="0:39.797">的</span></p><p begin="0:41.036" end="0:45.019" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:41.036" end="0:42.459">不相信我</span><span begin="0:42.459" end="0:43.484">看</span><span begin="0:43.484" end="0:44.142">到</span><span begin="0:44.142" end="0:45.019">的</span></p><p begin="0:46.313" end="0:54.931" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:46.313" end="0:47.641">硬要说裂</span><span begin="0:47.641" end="0:49.239">缝</span> <span begin="0:49.626" end="0:50.005">不</span><span begin="0:50.005" end="0:50.757">过</span><span begin="0:51.487" end="0:51.917">是</span><span begin="0:51.917" end="0:52.888">皱</span><span begin="0:52.888" end="0:54.931">褶</span></p></div><div begin="0:56.759" end="2:26.320" itunes:songPart="Chorus"><p begin="0:56.759" end="1:02.051" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:56.759" end="0:57.494">怎</span><span begin="0:57.494" end="0:58.054">么</span><span begin="0:58.054" end="1:00.725">先炽热的却先变冷</span><span begin="1:00.725" end="1:02.051">了</span></p><p begin="1:02.297" end="1:07.208" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.297" end="1:04.626">慢热的却停不了</span> <span begin="1:04.626" end="1:05.923">还在沸腾</span><span begin="1:05.923" end="1:07.208">着</span></p><p begin="1:07.493" end="1:11.774" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.493" end="1:09.755">看时光任性快跑</span> <span begin="1:09.755" end="1:11.122">随意就转</span><span begin="1:11.122" end="1:11.774">折</span></p><p begin="1:12.084" end="1:18.096" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.084" end="1:13.443">慢冷的人</span><span begin="1:13.443" end="1:14.477">啊</span> <span begin="1:14.660" end="1:15.709">会自我</span><span begin="1:15.709" end="1:16.391">折</span><span begin="1:16.391" end="1:18.096">磨</span></p><p begin="1:18.302" end="1:22.951" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:18.302" end="1:21.605">冲动的人向来听不见挽</span><span begin="1:21.605" end="1:22.951">留</span></p><p begin="1:23.178" end="1:28.338" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.178" end="1:26.826">这世界大得让你很难不旅</span><span begin="1:26.826" end="1:28.338">游</span></p><p begin="1:28.684" end="1:30.968" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:28.684" end="1:30.426">浪漫让你温</span><span begin="1:30.426" end="1:30.968">柔</span></p><p begin="1:31.305" end="1:37.798" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:31.305" end="1:33.092">也让你最惹</span><span begin="1:33.092" end="1:34.010">人</span><span begin="1:34.246" end="1:34.978">泪</span><span begin="1:34.978" end="1:37.798">流</span></p><p begin="1:38.536" end="1:43.848" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:38.536" end="1:39.235">怎</span><span begin="1:39.235" end="1:39.750">么</span><span begin="1:39.750" end="1:42.488">先炽热的却先变冷</span><span begin="1:42.488" end="1:43.848">了</span></p><p begin="1:44.023" end="1:48.944" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.023" end="1:46.352">慢热的却停不了</span> <span begin="1:46.352" end="1:47.674">还在沸腾</span><span begin="1:47.674" end="1:48.944">着</span></p><p begin="1:49.190" end="1:53.501" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.190" end="1:51.532">看时光任性快跑</span> <span begin="1:51.532" end="1:52.862">随意就转</span><span begin="1:52.862" end="1:53.501">折</span></p><p begin="1:53.840" end="1:59.552" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.840" end="1:55.194">慢冷的人</span><span begin="1:55.194" end="1:56.126">啊</span> <span begin="1:56.401" end="1:57.429">会自我</span><span begin="1:57.429" end="1:58.101">折</span><span begin="1:58.101" end="1:59.552">磨</span></p><p begin="1:59.975" end="2:04.654" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.975" end="2:03.325">冲动的人向来听不见挽</span><span begin="2:03.325" end="2:04.654">留</span></p><p begin="2:04.916" end="2:10.016" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.916" end="2:08.577">这世界大得让你很难不旅</span><span begin="2:08.577" end="2:10.016">游</span></p><p begin="2:10.404" end="2:12.648" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.404" end="2:12.168">浪漫让你温</span><span begin="2:12.168" end="2:12.648">柔</span></p><p begin="2:13.048" end="2:26.320" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:13.048" end="2:14.857">也让你最惹</span><span begin="2:14.857" end="2:17.677">人</span><span begin="2:19.531" end="2:20.542">泪</span><span begin="2:20.542" end="2:26.320">流</span></p></div></body></tt>